# gene_groups-hugo_hgnc is a research INSTANCE — generated data, run logs,
# intermediate outputs, and per-gene-group sub-runs. Not source code.
#
# Workflow templates are tracked in the sibling -COPYME directories:
#   ../gene_groups-COPYME/             (source-agnostic template)
#   ../gene_groups_hgnc-COPYME/        (HGNC-anchored template)
#
# Everything in this instance directory is treated as data. The .gitignore
# itself is the only tracked file (so the directory's presence is recorded).
*
!.gitignore
